\cf2 // SC3 has its own buffer Granulator, TGrains, where the type of algorithm shown above is coded into its own Ugen -- see its helpfile for more information on its arguments, from which the example below is adapted:\cf0 \
\
\cf2 // TGrains.ar(numChannels, trigger, bufnum, rate, centerPos, dur, pan, amp, interp)\cf0 \
