\cf0  \cf2 /* the following granulator adapted from one written by Brad Garton, who teaches at Columbia Univ.  The idea is the same as for the last granulator, but all of the granulation parameters are chosen stochastically from limits set from the GUI  -- the SCRangeSlider, which selects upper and lower limits of a range,  comes in handy here \
